Download nginx for windows (Thanks Jordan)

http://nginx-win.ecsds.eu/download/nginx%201.7.12.1%20Lizard.zip 

Unzip the file into a directory such as  c:\stream\nginx

Copy the nginx.conf (from this github) into that directory c:\stream\nginx

Turn off your local firewall or allow port 1935,1936,1937, and 1938

run nginx.exe 

Point your RTMP source to  (Cameras)

Source1      rtmp:\\IPaddressOfWidowsBox:1935\live1\cam
Source2      rtmp:\\IPaddressOfWidowsBox:1936\live2\cam
Source3      rtmp:\\IPaddressOfWidowsBox:1937\live3\cam
Source4      rtmp:\\IPaddressOfWidowsBox:1938\live4\cam

Add media source to OBS 

Source1      rtmp:\\IPaddressOfWidowsBox:1935\live1\cam
Source2      rtmp:\\IPaddressOfWidowsBox:1936\live2\cam
Source3      rtmp:\\IPaddressOfWidowsBox:1937\live3\cam
Source4      rtmp:\\IPaddressOfWidowsBox:1938\live4\cam
